(Ameen)

Is Liye Bahot Zaroori Hai Ke Musalmaan Apni Dunyawi Mashguliyan Ke Saath Kuchh Waqt Nikaal Kar Kam Az Kam Itna Ilm Haasil Kare Jo Us Par Farz Hai Aur Koshish Kare Ke Ziyaada Se Ziyaada Ilm Haasil Kare Aur Us Par Amal Kare.
---*---*--*--*---*---
Allah Ta'ala se Dua hai ke Jo Log Masjid Ku Banaye aur Aabaad  Karte Hai Allah Une Aabaad Kare aur une ki Maghfirat kare..
(Ameen)
(Suma Ameen )

"DEEN" is. Therefore, it is necessary for every Muslim to implement the law of Allah Ta'ala and to obey Hazrat Muhammad  in every aspect of his life and to think of making people like him.
That is why it is very important for Muslims to spend some time in their worldly activities and gain as much knowledge as possible which is their duty on us and try to gain more and more knowledge and apply it on us.
